'''Port-Esta''' was the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Vestar/Legends|Vestar]] and served as the base of operations for the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Lightning Battalion]] during the group's [[Icarii Campaign|campaign]] against the [[Icarii]].

